T03-water animal
I was given a 6 gallon nano-reef aquarium in the spring of 2006, and I have tried to maintain it. Of the original coral colonies, the pink Pumping Xinias and the Star Polyps have so far survived. This is a log of the condition in the coral tank, started in ernest November 1997. Long term goal is to create a good time based account of it's state.
